Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.61,0:28:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Poi potrò sposarvi tutte, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.81,0:28:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.82,0:28:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.95,0:28:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.94,0:28:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.65,0:28:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Non posso proprio sceglierne solo una.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.49,0:28:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Perché... Onee-chan, \Nio vi amo tutte tanto!